---
title: Bacon and Cheese Linguine with creme fraiche and cherry tomatoes
description: This rapid-to-prepare pasta dish is meaty, cheesy and deliciously rich. Bacon adds saltiness and bite which pairs wonderfully with the creamy cheesy sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R04_W29_IE_IECFQP15109-4_remove_Main_1_high-66381837.jpg
